WARNING: May cause seizes! Please view at your own risk!

The photo used to make this GIF is of the stars over some small beach in Maui that I happen stumbled upon one night. I took the truck my family and I were renting to meet a very beautiful woman I met while snoring that morning. Unfortunately she worked all day and fell asleep as soon as she got home... But, at I got this photo -- and took her out two-stepping on another beach the next night
